OL,3,CBuilder who killed stranger in
OL,4,Cunprovoked one-punch attack jailed
OL,6,FA builder who killed a man with what
OL,7,Fhe claimed was a slap in an unprovoked
OL,8,Fattack just seven months after he was
OL,9,Fsentenced over a similar assault has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed.
OL,12,FMax Skidmore, 37, caused 55-year-old
OL,13,FEddie Roberts fatal head injuries when
OL,14,Fhe floored him with a single punch in
OL,15,FLincoln on the night of 8 December
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,18,FSkidmore, of Lytton Street, Lincoln,
OL,19,Fclaimed he had merely slapped Mr
OL,20,FRoberts to "shoo him off".
