OL,3,CBuilder who killed stranger in
OL,4,Cunprovoked one-punch attack jailed
OL,6,FBut a judge at Lincoln Crown Court
OL,7,Frejected his claim after an eye
OL,8,Fwitness described the blow as a punch.
OL,10,FThe court heard the incident happened
OL,11,Fseven months after Skidmore was given
OL,12,Fa 12-month conditional discharge for
OL,13,Fan assault in a pub on Lincoln High
OL,14,FStreet.
OL,16,FSkidmore, a trained boxer, had claimed
OL,17,Fat the time that he had slapped the
OL,18,Fvictim.
