OL,3,CBuilder who killed stranger in
OL,4,Cunprovoked one-punch attack jailed
OL,6,FSkidmore, who did not know the victim,
OL,7,Ftold the court he had been celebrating
OL,8,Fhis 37th birthday and had visited a
OL,9,Fnumber of pubs before driving off in
OL,10,Fhis van to find his girlfriend.
OL,12,FWitnesses described him driving at
OL,13,Fspeed around the streets before he
OL,14,Fparked up in Carholme Road, where Mr
OL,15,FRoberts was walking.
OL,17,FThe judge described Skidmore's
OL,18,Fbehaviour as an "incident waiting to
OL,19,Fhappen."
