OL,3,CBuilder who killed stranger in
OL,4,Cunprovoked one-punch attack jailed
OL,6,F"You were two and half times over the
OL,7,Flimit as you drove around in an angry
OL,8,Fand aggressive mood," Judge Sjolin
OL,9,FKnight said.
OL,11,FRight-handed Skidmore claimed he had
OL,12,Fused his left hand to slap Mr Roberts.
OL,14,FBut he later accepted that police
OL,15,Ffound no injury to his left hand.
OL,17,FIn a victim impact statement, Mr
OL,18,FRoberts' son Sean described his father
OL,19,Fas "hilaraious, loving, caring and as
OL,20,Fstubborn as they come".
