OL,3,CBuilder who killed stranger in
OL,4,Cunprovoked one-punch attack jailed
OL,6,FHe added: "He was a hard worker who
OL,7,Fcould turn his hand to anything. I
OL,8,Fhaven't just lost a father, I've lost
OL,9,Fa brother, a confidant, a best friend,
OL,10,Fmy right hand."
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Andy McWatt, of
OL,13,FLincolnshire Police, said: "It's one
OL,14,Fof the most tragic cases. Eddie was a
OL,15,Fcompletely innocent party and this was
OL,16,Fdevastating for everybody."
OL,18,FHe added: "It just shows you how
OL,19,Ffragile life is and how one punch can
OL,20,Fchange families' lives forever."
